text: I read somewhere where Godzilla, in this new movie, is described as mankind's "savior." Obviously, to generate excitement, the trailer makes it look like it's another "Cloverfield," but I believe, on several instances, you can clearly see a second monster in the various clips. First, the glowing appendage that the soldiers find underground. Second, the thing that's flying and swats the airplanes from the sky and then plunges into the ocean. Third, the glowing appendage that slams down on the concrete. And fourth, when the soldiers on the roof shoots the red lights into the sky, revealing a monster that looks nothing like Godzilla. I think what you'll see is Godzilla fighting another entity (alien?) inside at least one American city. I could be wrong, but this looks pretty bad ass.
